"version": "1.0.4",
"title": "5685: fathers, responsibilities of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5685",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Fathers have a responsibility to love, instruct and discipline their children in the ways of the Lord. In return they are to be honoured and obeyed by their children.</p>\n<h2>The role of fathers</h2>\n<h3>To love and care for their children</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps103:13\">PSA 103:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut1:31\">DEU 1:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job1:4-Job1:5\">JOB 1:4–1:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:9-Matt7:11\">MAT 7:9–7:11</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:11-Luke11:13\">LUK 11:11–11:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:21\">COL 3:21</a></p>\n<h3>To discipline their children</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov13:24\">PRO 13:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:5\">DEU 8:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut21:18-Deut21:21\">DEU 21:18–21:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:11-Prov3:12\">PRO 3:11–3:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:5\">PRO 15:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov19:18\">PRO 19:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov22:15\">PRO 22:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov23:13\">PRO 23:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov29:15\">PRO 29:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim3:2-1Tim3:5\">1TI 3:2–3:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim3:12\">1TI 3:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:7-Heb12:11\">HEB 12:7–12:11</a></p>\n<h3>To instruct their children</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:2-Ps78:8\">PSA 78:2–78:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:9\">DEU 4:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:6-Deut6:7\">DEU 6:6–6:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:20-Deut6:24\">DEU 6:20–6:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut11:18-Deut11:21\">DEU 11:18–11:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut31:13\">DEU 31:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov13:1\">PRO 13:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov22:6\">PRO 22:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:4\">EPH 6:4</a></p>\n<h2>The rights of fathers</h2>\n<h3>To be honoured by their children</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:12\">EXO 20:12</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:16\">DEU 5:16</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:3\">LEV 19:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:4\">MAT 15:4</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:10\">MRK 7:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod21:17\">EXO 21:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:17-Matt19:19\">MAT 19:17–19:19</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:18-Mark10:19\">MRK 10:18–10:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:19-Luke18:20\">LUK 18:19–18:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:2-Eph6:3\">EPH 6:2–6:3</a></p>\n<h3>To be obeyed by their children</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:20\">COL 3:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut21:18-Deut21:21\">DEU 21:18–21:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov6:20\">PRO 6:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov8:32\">PRO 8:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:51\">LUK 2:51</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:1\">EPH 6:1</a></p>\n<h3>To be heeded by their children</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov23:22\">PRO 23:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov1:8\">PRO 1:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov4:1\">PRO 4:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov4:10\">PRO 4:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov13:1\">PRO 13:1</a></p>\n<h2>The joy of fathers</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov23:24\">PRO 23:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps127:3-Ps127:5\">PSA 127:3–127:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps128:3-Ps128:4\">PSA 128:3–128:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:1\">PRO 10:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov28:7\">PRO 28:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov29:3\">PRO 29:3</a></p>\n<h2>The sorrow of fathers</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov17:21\">PRO 17:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:1\">PRO 10:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov17:25\">PRO 17:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov19:13\">PRO 19:13</a></p>\n<h2>The roles of fathers-in-law</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen29:21-Gen29:23\">GEN 29:21–29:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen31:39-Gen31:42\">GEN 31:39–31:42</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod3:1\">EXO 3:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod18:14-Exod18:27\">EXO 18:14–18:27</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg19:3-Judg19:9\">JDG 19:3–19:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam4:19-1Sam4:21\">1SA 4:19–4:21</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John18:13\">JHN 18:13</a></p>\n<h2>Children's responsibility to honour their parents</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:12\">EXO 20:12</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:16\">DEU 5:16</a> <em>“Honour” implies respect, obedience and care for the parents' needs.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:3\">LEV 19:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:19\">MAT 19:19</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:19\">MRK 10:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:20\">LUK 18:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:1-Eph6:3\">EPH 6:1–6:3</a></p>\n<h2>Penalties for disobeying parents</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod21:15\">EXO 21:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod21:17\">EXO 21:17</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut21:18-Deut21:21\">DEU 21:18–21:21</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov20:20\">PRO 20:20</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:4-Matt15:6\">MAT 15:4–15:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:10-Mark7:13\">MRK 7:10–7:13</a></p>\n<h2>The ministry of Jesus Christ may produce conflict within families</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:53\">LUK 12:53</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:35-Matt10:36\">MAT 10:35–10:36</a></p>\n<h2>Following Jesus Christ involves a commitment to him even deeper than love of one's parents</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:37\">MAT 10:37</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke14:26\">LUK 14:26</a></p>",
